            "body": "It works for me on Cython 3.0.9 with Python 3.11.5.\r\n\r\nHave you set the directive `# cython: binding = False` somewhere? That turns off a lot of introspection and means that `inspect.isgeneratorfunction` won't work on them. It's on by default though.",
